<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>,</p>

<p>Someone has invited you to ODI Signon, you can accept it through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Accept invitation', accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @resource.invitation_token) %></p>

<p>If you don't want to accept the invitation, please ignore this email.<br />
Your account won't be created until you access the link above and set your passphrase.</p>
<p>If you do not access the link within two weeks, it will expire.</p>
